div.p:
4227. The following are the minutes of the meeting held in Lisbon on August 18 [19] (to Kkad and AGWar for the Combined Chiefs of Staff and to USFor for British Chiefs of Staff signed Eisenhower cite fhcos . Reference Naf 333.This message, dated August 20, 1943, was a brief summary of the Lisbon meeting with Castellano. For text, see Eisenhower Papers, p. 1349. This is Naf 334.) with the following present:
Sir Ronald Campbell, British Ambassador;
Mr George F. Kennan, American Chargé dAffaires;
General Castellano, Italian Army;
Mr Montanari, Interpreter;
Major General William [Walter] B Smith, US Army;
Brigadier Strong, British Army.
